        "\n",
        "![Linear regression is a single-layer neural network.](../M08_lecture01_figures/singleneuron.svg){#fig-single_neuron width=80%, fig-align=\"center\" fig-alt=\"A diagram of a single neuron with multiple inputs and one output.\"}\n",
